reviewText: Somehow I missed the fact that this video is only 10 minutes long.  For the price, I expected more.  I expected something like a documentary.  And the quality of the video is not great.  On the plus side, you do get some excellent views of the impressive falls - but somehow the video overall falls short.

this dvd might be interesting for tourists, before going there. you can get a good overview in just 10 min. really nice views of the falls, from the most interesting outlooks - on both sides, argentina and brazil. really impressive pictures.
